            .aboutUsContentHolder
                h1.script-text We care about you
                h1 We care about you
                p Welcome to Mandleleni, a funeral parlour and catering company based in Mpumalanga Nelspruit. Our company was founded in 2020 with a passion for providing high-quality funeral and catering services to the community. We understand that losing a loved one is a difficult time, and that's why we strive to make the process as smooth and stress-free as possible. Our experienced funeral directors are available 24/7 to assist you with all your funeral arrangements, from choosing the perfect casket to arranging the funeral service. We offer a range of funeral packages to suit your budget, as well as customised options to cater to your specific needs.
                p In addition to our funeral services, we also offer catering services for all types of events, including weddings, parties, and corporate functions. Our talented chefs use only the freshest ingredients to create delicious, mouth-watering meals that will impress your guests. We can accommodate any dietary requirements or preferences, and we offer a variety of menu options to suit your taste and budget. At Mandleleni, we pride ourselves on providing exceptional customer service and attention to detail. We understand the importance of every event we cater for, and we strive to exceed your expectations every time. Contact us today to find out how we can assist you with your funeral or catering needs.

